I bought this for my 6 & 8 year old daughters.  They tell me that this movie teaches a lot about marine animals and the friendship between a boy and a dolphin.  It is appropriate for their age group and they think it is very entertaining.  Good price for this 2-DVD bundle!

Both movies are outstanding to watch. Winter is the
famous dolphin and you can go to their web site to see her today.
**(The pelican is a real "pesty" bird that makes you laugh.)
All the characters did a terrific job in both movies! It
makes you appreciate wildlife. Veterans will enjoy these
movies because the have survived the war with missing
legs and arms-Winter is a handicapped dolphin without a tail.
You feel a warm fuzzy feeling from both movies~~Worth watching!
